        "content": "<p>pchickey <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12774#issuecomment-4056710264\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12774\">issue #12774</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Wasmtime binaries are published to GitHub releases, and the <code>cargo binstall</code> tool automates fetching and installing those locally.</p>\n<p><div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">hickey</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">KVKD0WG7VF</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">src</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">nginx</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">wasm</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"o\">%</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">cargo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">binstall</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">wasmtime</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">cli</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">INFO</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">resolve</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Resolving</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">package</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"na\">wasmtime</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">cli</span><span class=\"o\">'</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">WARN</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">The</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">package</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">wasmtime</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">cli</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v42</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"mf\">0.1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">aarch64</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">apple</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">darwin</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">has</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">been</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">downloaded</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">from</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">github</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">com</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">INFO</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">This</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">will</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">install</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">following</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">binaries</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">INFO</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">wasmtime</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">Users</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">hickey</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">cargo</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bin</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">wasmtime</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Do</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">you</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">wish</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">continue</span><span class=\"o\">?</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">yes</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">no</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">INFO</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Installing</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">binaries</span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">INFO</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Done</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mf\">6.135038625</span><span class=\"n\">s</span>\n</code></pre></div><br>\n</p>\n</blockquote>",
